trans-unit.source: Represents a collection of all [Target](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md) elements in a project.
Adds a new [Target](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md) element to the end of the project.
The <xref uid="langword_csharp_Name" name="Name" href=""></xref> attribute of the new <xref uid="langword_csharp_Target" name="Target" href=""></xref> element.
A <xref href="Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.Target"></xref> object representing the created `Target` element.
Copies the entire <xref href="Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.TargetCollection"></xref> to a compatible one-dimensional <xref:System.Array>, starting at the specified index of the target array.
The one-dimensional <xref:System.Array> that is the destination of the elements copied from <xref href="Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.TargetCollection"></xref>.
The <xref:System.Array> must have zero-based indexing.
The zero-based index in `array` at which copying begins.
Gets a value indicating the number of <xref href="Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.Target"></xref> objects in the <xref href="Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.TargetCollection"></xref>.
Each <xref:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.Target> object in the collection represents a element in the project.
An integer value representing the number of <xref href="Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.Target"></xref> objects in the collection.
Determines whether the specified <xref href="Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.Target"></xref> exists in the <xref href="Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.TargetCollection"></xref>.
The <xref uid="langword_csharp_Name" name="Name" href=""></xref> attribute of the Target element to search for.
<xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> if the `Target` element exists; otherwise, <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
Gets an enumerator that iterates through the <xref href="Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.TargetCollection"></xref>.

This method allows the caller to use the `foreach` statement of the C# language (`for each` in [!INCLUDE[vbprvb](~/add/includes/vbprvb-md.md)]) to iterate through the individual <xref:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.Target> objects in the <xref:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.TargetCollection>.
An <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator> for the entire <xref href="Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.TargetCollection"></xref>.
Gets a value indicating whether access to the <xref href="Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.TargetCollection"></xref> is synchronized (thread safe).

<xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> if access to the <xref href="Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.TargetCollection"></xref> is synchronized (thread safe); otherwise, <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
The default is <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
Gets the specified <xref href="Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.Target"></xref> object in the <xref href="Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.TargetCollection"></xref>.
A <xref:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.Target> object represents a `Target` element in the project.
The <xref uid="langword_csharp_Name" name="Name" href=""></xref> attribute of the Target element in the collection.
The object that contains the property value specified by index.
Removes the specified [Target](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md) element from the project.
The <xref uid="langword_csharp_Name" name="Name" href=""></xref> attribute of the <xref uid="langword_csharp_Target" name="Target" href=""></xref> element to remove.
Gets an object that can be used to synchronize access to the <xref href="Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.TargetCollection"></xref>.
An object that can be used to synchronize access to the <xref href="Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.TargetCollection"></xref>.
